<span data-as="p">Two common fixes:</span>
<ol>
<li>Put the missing keys in <code>~/.openclaw/.env</code> so they’re picked up even when the service doesn’t inherit your shell env.</li>
<li>Enable shell import (opt-in convenience):</li>
</ol>
