<span data-as="p">Tip: <code>/model status</code> shows which agent is active, which <code>auth-profiles.json</code> file is being used, and which auth profile will be tried next.
It also shows the configured provider endpoint (<code>baseUrl</code>) and API mode (<code>api</code>) when available.</span>
<span data-as="p"><strong>How do I unpin a profile I set with profile</strong></span>
<span data-as="p">Re-run <code>/model</code> <strong>without</strong> the <code>@profile</code> suffix:</span>
