<span data-as="p">Service/supervisor logs (when the gateway runs via launchd/systemd):</span>
<ul>
<li>macOS: <code>$OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR/logs/gateway.log</code> and <code>gateway.err.log</code> (default: <code>~/.openclaw/logs/...</code>; profiles use <code>~/.openclaw-&lt;profile&gt;/logs/...</code>)</li>
<li>Linux: <code>journalctl --user -u openclaw-gateway[-&lt;profile&gt;].service -n 200 --no-pager</code></li>
<li>Windows: <code>schtasks /Query /TN &quot;OpenClaw Gateway (&lt;profile&gt;)&quot; /V /FO LIST</code></li>
</ul>
<span data-as="p">See <a class="link" href="../gateway/troubleshooting#log-locations">Troubleshooting</a> for more.</span>
