<span data-as="p">There are <strong>two Windows install modes</strong>:</span>
<span data-as="p"><strong>1) WSL2 (recommended):</strong> the Gateway runs inside Linux.</span>
<span data-as="p">Open PowerShell, enter WSL, then restart:</span>
