<span data-as="p">If you want immediate access, allowlist your sender id or set <code>dmPolicy: &quot;open&quot;</code>
for that account.</span>
<h3 class="flex whitespace-pre-wrap group font-semibold" id="whatsapp-will-it-message-my-contacts-how-does-pairing-work"><div class="absolute" tabindex="-1"><a href="faq#whatsapp-will-it-message-my-contacts-how-does-pairing-work" class="-ml-10 flex items-center opacity-0 border-0 group-hover:opacity-100 focus:opacity-100 focus:outline-0 group/link" aria-label="Navigate to header">​<div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-white/50 dark:bg-background-dark dark:brightness-[1.35] dark:ring-1 dark:hover:brightness-150 bg-white ring-1 ring-gray-400/30 dark:ring-gray-700/25 hover:ring-gray-400/60 dark:hover:ring-white/20 group-focus/link:border-2 group-focus/link:border-primary dark:group-focus/link:border-primary-light"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="gray" height="12px" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><path d="M0 256C0 167.6 71.6 96 160 96h72c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H160C98.1 144 48 194.1 48 256s50.1 112 112 112h72c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H160C71.6 416 0 344.4 0 256zm576 0c0 88.4-71.6 160-160 160H344c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24h72c61.9 0 112-50.1 112-112s-50.1-112-112-112H344c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24h72c88.4 0 160 71.6 160 160zM184 232H392c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24s-10.7 24-24 24H184c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24s10.7-24 24-24z"></path></svg></div></a></div><span class="cursor-pointer">WhatsApp will it message my contacts How does pairing work</span></h3>
<span data-as="p">No. Default WhatsApp DM policy is <strong>pairing</strong>. Unknown senders only get a pairing code and their message is <strong>not processed</strong>. OpenClaw only replies to chats it receives or to explicit sends you trigger.</span>
